Interface VideoOutputEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DirectMediaPlayerComponent, EmbeddedMediaListPlayerComponent, EmbeddedMediaPlayerComponent
    Deprecated. 
    use MediaPlayerEventListener.videoOutput(MediaPlayer, int) instead, this class will be removed in vlcj 1.3.0

    public interface VideoOutputEventListener
    Specification for a component that is interested in receiving video output event notifications from the media player.
